title: Milo Manara: The Ape (Catalan Communications)
description:
English edition published by Catalan Communications 1986.

Original edition published in 1976.

Writing: Silverio Pisu
Art: Milo Manara

An early book by Milo Manara based on the Chinese Monkey King (Sun Wukong) from Journey to the West. 

Milo Manara's style was a lot more wild and psychedelic looking at this state but his knack for drawing women was indeed evident.

Great book!
